snippet.title: Commandos: Origin - Gameplay Overview Trailer  | gamescom 2024
snippet.description:
Build impenetrable bases and infiltrate enemy compounds in Claymore Game Studios sequel real-time tactics game, Commandos Origin, coming to Xbox One, Xbox Series X/S, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, and PC in 2024.
